CatDescriptText: Headline for related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 28, 1958, page A11, reads: "Alphas Host Brilliant 30th Anniversary Ball"
TitMainTitle: Two women and two men, including woman on left wearing light colored ball gown with single sheer short sleeve, corsage, and light colored gloves, man on right wearing eyeglasses, dark pants, light colored suit jacket and button down collared shirt, dark bow tie and sash with light colored strip, seated on stone half wall, gathered on exterior steps of Hotel Webster Hall for the Alpha Phi Alpha 30th Anniversary ball
